        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks RT for his letter and MS.</p>
            <p>Is astonished by the different forms of orchids he describes.</p>
            <p>Urges RT to describe and experiment with two or three of the more distinct genera.</p>
            <p>"I believe, or am inclined to believe in one or very few primordial forms, from community of structure and early embryonic resemblances in each great class."</p>
        </abstract>
